## 🔧 v9.3 설계: 여섯 가지 패턴

### 패턴 1️⃣: 공유 설정 (Shared Configuration)

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
struct SecurityConfig {
    active_protocol: String,
    max_connections: usize,
}

struct AdminPanel {
    name: String,
    config: Rc<RefCell<SecurityConfig>>,
}

impl AdminPanel {
    fn new(name: &str, config: Rc<RefCell<SecurityConfig>>) -> Self {
        Self {
            name: String::from(name),
            config,
        }
    }

    /// 현재 설정을 읽습니다 (불변 접근)
    fn read_config(&self) -> String {
        let cfg = self.config.borrow();
        format!("Protocol: {}, Connections: {}",
            cfg.active_protocol, cfg.max_connections)
    }

    /// 설정을 변경합니다 (가변 접근)
    fn update_protocol(&self, protocol: &str) {
        self.config.borrow_mut().active_protocol = String::from(protocol);
    }

    fn get_name(&self) -> &str {
        &self.name
    }
}
```

### 패턴 2️⃣: 양방향 트리 (Bidirectional Tree)

```rust
#[derive(Debug)]
struct TreeNode {
    value: i32,
    parent: Option<Rc<RefCell<TreeNode>>>,
    children: Vec<Rc<RefCell<TreeNode>>>,
}

impl TreeNode {
    fn new(value: i32) -> Rc<RefCell<Self>> {
        Rc::new(RefCell::new(Self {
            value,
            parent: None,
            children: Vec::new(),
        }))
    }

    fn add_child(parent: &Rc<RefCell<TreeNode>>,
                 child: Rc<RefCell<TreeNode>>) {
        parent.borrow_mut().children.push(Rc::clone(&child));
        child.borrow_mut().parent = Some(Rc::clone(parent));
    }

    fn get_value(&self) -> i32 {
        self.value
    }
}
```

### 패턴 3️⃣: 그래프 네트워크 (Graph Network)

```rust
struct GraphNode {
    id: usize,
    neighbors: Vec<Rc<RefCell<GraphNode>>>,
}

impl GraphNode {
    fn new(id: usize) -> Rc<RefCell<Self>> {
        Rc::new(RefCell::new(Self {
            id,
            neighbors: Vec::new(),
        }))
    }

    fn connect(from: &Rc<RefCell<GraphNode>>,
               to: Rc<RefCell<GraphNode>>) {
        from.borrow_mut().neighbors.push(to);
    }
}
```

### 패턴 4️⃣: 동적 상태 머신 (Dynamic State Machine)

```rust
#[derive(Clone, Debug)]
enum State {
    Idle,
    Running,
    Paused,
    Stopped,
}

struct StateMachine {
    state: Rc<RefCell<State>>,
}

impl StateMachine {
    fn new() -> Self {
        Self {
            state: Rc::new(RefCell::new(State::Idle)),
        }
    }

    fn transition(&self, new_state: State) {
        *self.state.borrow_mut() = new_state;
    }

    fn is_running(&self) -> bool {
        matches!(*self.state.borrow(), State::Running)
    }
}
```

### 패턴 5️⃣: 공유 카운터 (Shared Counter)

```rust
struct SharedCounter {
    count: Rc<RefCell<i32>>,
}

impl Clone for SharedCounter {
    fn clone(&self) -> Self {
        Self {
            count: Rc::clone(&self.count),
        }
    }
}

impl SharedCounter {
    fn new() -> Self {
        Self {
            count: Rc::new(RefCell::new(0)),
        }
    }

    fn increment(&self) {
        *self.count.borrow_mut() += 1;
    }

    fn get(&self) -> i32 {
        *self.count.borrow()
    }
}
```

### 패턴 6️⃣: 리스너 등록 (Observer Pattern)

```rust
type Listener = Box<dyn Fn(String) + 'static>;

struct EventDispatcher {
    listeners: Rc<RefCell<Vec<Listener>>>,
}

impl EventDispatcher {
    fn new() -> Self {
        Self {
            listeners: Rc::new(RefCell::new(Vec::new())),
        }
    }

    fn subscribe<F>(&self, listener: F)
    where
        F: Fn(String) + 'static,
    {
        self.listeners
            .borrow_mut()
            .push(Box::new(listener));
    }

    fn emit(&self, event: String) {
        for listener in self.listeners.borrow().iter() {
            listener(event.clone());
        }
    }
}
```

