## 🏗️ v9.3 실전 설계: Gogs 보안 노드 네트워크

### 설계 구조: 분산 제어 시스템

```rust
#[derive(Debug, Clone)]
struct SecurityConfig {
    active_protocol: String,
    encryption_level: u32,
}

#[derive(Debug)]
struct SecurityNode {
    node_id: usize,
    config: Rc<RefCell<SecurityConfig>>,
    neighbors: Vec<Rc<RefCell<SecurityNode>>>,
}

impl SecurityNode {
    fn new(node_id: usize,
           config: Rc<RefCell<SecurityConfig>>) -> Rc<RefCell<Self>> {
        Rc::new(RefCell::new(Self {
            node_id,
            config,
            neighbors: Vec::new(),
        }))
    }

    fn get_node_id(&self) -> usize {
        self.node_id
    }

    fn read_config(&self) -> String {
        let cfg = self.config.borrow();
        format!("Protocol: {}, Level: {}",
            cfg.active_protocol, cfg.encryption_level)
    }

    fn update_config(&self, protocol: &str, level: u32) {
        let mut cfg = self.config.borrow_mut();
        cfg.active_protocol = String::from(protocol);
        cfg.encryption_level = level;
    }

    fn connect_to(from: &Rc<RefCell<SecurityNode>>,
                  to: Rc<RefCell<SecurityNode>>) {
        from.borrow_mut().neighbors.push(to);
    }

    fn get_neighbor_count(&self) -> usize {
        self.neighbors.len()
    }
}
```

### 메모리 추적 과정

```
초기 상태:
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│ Rc<RefCell<SecurityConfig>>     │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ RefCount: 3 (3개 노드가 소유)   │
│ active_protocol: "TLS_1.3"      │
│ encryption_level: 256           │
└─────────────────────────────────┘
    ▲          ▲          ▲
    │          │          │
  node1      node2      node3

node2가 설정 변경:
node2.update_config("TLS_1.2", 128);

즉시 반영됨:
node1.read_config()  → "Protocol: TLS_1.2, Level: 128"
node3.read_config()  → "Protocol: TLS_1.2, Level: 128"
```

